subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened national capacities for implementation of HIV funds and programmes, including those financed through multilateral initiatives like the Global Fund to fight AIDS, Tuberculosis, and Malaria
subproject.description:
Project outputs:
- Public health care sector capacities built to reduce the burden of TB in Tajikistan by 2015 in line with the MDGs and "Stop TB partnership" targets

subproject.title: TB Prevention &Control Program
